{"tid":1952961,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《榮耀世紀》即將回歸 刪檔封測召集展開3/24/2020","createTime":"2020-04-01T02:00:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T15:31:09.000Z","uid":24626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"11be367f4c5eac22fe5da41e70964dac3f5875c4","tid":1952961,"uid":24626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T02:00:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/91060953_121545456144217_6780620575644581888_n.jpg?_nc_cat=108&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=zhmxKQ9XdvUAX8-5_Yw&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-2.fna&amp;oh=509f0a7638f52a619cc55240257273eb&amp;oe=5EA9883B\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F91060953_121545456144217_6780620575644581888_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D108%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3DzhmxKQ9XdvUAX8-5_Yw%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-2.fna%26oh%3D509f0a7638f52a619cc55240257273eb%26oe%3D5EA9883B&h=8a24de4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCGNET遊戲平台宣佈與GNISOFT攜手合作，正式取得《榮耀世紀》香港、台灣的兩地代理權，並將於4月3日至4月7日進行刪檔封測。<br />\n<br />\n《榮耀世紀》自面世至今已逾十五年，營運團隊為讓各位挑戰者能夠快速適應上手，除了對遊戲設定進行全面優化，更特意新增「自動狩獵」、「成長指南」、以及「任務追蹤」等多項輔助功能。<br />\n《榮耀世紀》將於4月3日至4月7日進行刪檔封測，即日起同步開放「事前登錄」，凡完成登錄的挑戰者均可在公測時獲得獎勵道具一份。<br />\n<br />\n封測召集頁面: <a href=\"http://www.cdonline.hk/event/closedbeta\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdonline.hk%2Fevent%2Fclosedbeta&d=J1zZABjvT6n5gtW5jiJIhrTKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=211eef34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.cdonline.hk/event/closedbeta</a><br />\n事前登錄活動: <a href=\"http://www.cdonline.hk/event/closedbeta#reserve\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdonline.hk%2Fevent%2Fclosedbeta%23reserve&d=J1zZABjvT6n5gtW5jiJIhrTKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=9b1e3e89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.cdonline.hk/event/closedbeta#reserve</a><br />\n<br />\n仲以為係愚人節 原來又係穢土轉生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無人記得點玩?"},{"pid":"afc7b60f2d5532c43852fdb69628cffef461470d","tid":1952961,"uid":17971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T15:31:09.000Z","msg":"執完又開開完又執 轉過幾間代理<br />\n以前黎講算好玩"}]}